The '''Eriadu stealth unit''' or the '''Eriadu prototype stealth module''' was a sophisticated and expert camouflage [[Stealth field generator/Legends|stealth mode]] unit employed during the time of the [[Old Sith Wars]]. Similarly to other stealth units, combat would disrupt the field, while ordinary tasks would not.

==Appearances==
*''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic]]'' {{1st}}
*''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic II: The Sith Lords]]''

